    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I'm not sure I can just pretend it isn't there. It feels so heavy. Every time they come over to help me with something, I can see it in their eyes... they're just exhausted. I hate being the reason they can't enjoy their own lives. It feels like the more I stay, the more I'm just taking from them.",
