    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just wish i could find a way to make it stop for them. if i wasn't around, they could finally breathe and just be happy without worrying if i've fallen or if i'm in pain. wouldn't it be more selfless to just... step aside? to let them have their lives back without the constant weight of me?",
